.5158, 92.9472, 92.3233, 91.2357, 90.1772, 90.0054, 90.1716, 90.2782, 88.8563, 89.3064, 89.6544, 89.3619, 88.0744, 87.4479, 88.5497, 89.3991, 89.863, 89.1055, 90.5011, 89.0209, 89.6584, 90.3154, 90.2963, 90.399, 90.4353, 90.3603, 89.9153, 91.3439, 91.8943, 91.9774, 94.1367, 94.5759, 93.2538, 92.6199, 92.6107, 92.3089, 91.2494, 92.7094, 92.0248, 92.5188, 92.1773, 92.61, 90.9995, 91.4356, 91.1839, 91.5528, 92.0408, 92.6637, 92.491, 91.8886, 93.6421, 94.7425, 96.1974, 96.801, 97.8241, 97.7435, 97.2699, 98.2142, 98.7377, 99.0459, 100.8176, 100.1234, 100.6202, 102.6453, 103.4129, 104.6422, 104.2457, 103.51, 105.7371, 106.3457, 106.8995, 105.8012, 104.0311, 105.0892, 104.679, 105.5494, 105.9292, 107.514, 107.5127, 108.1723, 109.1148, 109.3329, 110.4783, 110.89, 111.9071, 113.9104, 114.0651, 111.7109, 113.2336, 114.5289, 114.355, 115.9629, 116.2851, 114.4115, 114.4549, 115.2556, 115.696, 114.7928, 115.6143, 116.7661, 116.1145, 116.7432, 116.6184, 116.8078, 114.0918, 113.9892, 115.3152, 114.8445, 115.3298, 114.9957, 115.4856, 115.2919, 115.0602, 117.4488, 119.1757, 117.2587, 116.6318, 116.7685, 120.9166, 124.3483, 123.3216, 124.4151, 130.0661, 130.8246, 128.0557, 133.0246, 131.7875, 133.4041, 132.308, 132.8195, 135.3021, 138.7393, 139.0367, 135.734, 135.2131, 133.118, 134.9233, 134.8601, 133.3339, 134.0068, 131.983], "summary_html": "<h1>库存基本面与动量技术面共振策略</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略结合商品期货的库存基本面信号与价格动量技术面信号，通过\"双因子分组\"(Double-Sort)方法筛选多空品种。核心逻辑是：低库存偏离度 + 高历史动量的品种做多，高库存偏离度 + 低历史动量的品种做空。库存偏离度捕捉基本面驱动力（库存偏低→价格上行压力），动量信号捕捉短期趋势延续。两个信号弱相关但各有优势，共振后策略稳健性和风险调整收益显著提升。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.67</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.8%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.09</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2894</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.73</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.31</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.81 / 0.65</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.24</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.29</span></td><td>0.46</td><td>1.0</td><td>1.51</td><td>0.46</td><td>1.06</td><td>1.78</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.23</span></td><td>0.94</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.45</span></td><td>1.6</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.05</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 15 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 15 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2896</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>40.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>16.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>库存偏离度因子</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Stock\\_Dev}_i = \\frac{\\text{Inventory}_{i,t}}{\\frac{1}{R_s}\\sum_{k=0}^{R_s-1}\\text{Inventory}_{i,t-k}}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">R_s</span> 为库存移动平均窗口（排序期），<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Inventory}</span> 为品种库存数据（优先使用 <code>inventory_21</code>，缺失时用 <code>receipt</code> 替代）。</p>\n<p><strong>动量因子</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Mom}_{i,t} = \\frac{P_{i,t}}{P_{i,t-R_m}} - 1</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">R_m</span> 为动量回看期。</p>\n<p><strong>Stock-Mom 共振信号</strong>: 1. 按 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Stock\\_Dev}</span> 截面排名，分为低库存组（前40%）、高库存组（后40%）、中间组（20%） 2. 在低库存组内按 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Mom}</span> 排序，取上半部分做多（占总品种20%） 3. 在高库存组内按 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{Mom}</span> 排序，取下半部分做空（占总品种20%）</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.45，换手率0.68极高，离散+1/-1信号频繁翻转</td><td>改用连续信号(rank_to_continuous)；增加hold期10天；扩展参数网格</td><td>信号质量差但方向正确</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>：连续化+延长持仓期后 Sharpe 跃升至 0.94</td><td>增加 Rs80/100、Rm10/20、H10/15/20 的网格搜索；新增combo加权变体和IC gate变体</td><td>Sharpe 0.94，stock_mom_Rs80_Rm10_H15 胜出</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>已通过，尝试进一步优化</td><td>聚焦胜出参数区间(Rs60-100)；添加_cs/_ts归一化变体；IC gate过滤弱品种</td><td>Sharpe 维持0.94，cs/ts未提升（信号本身已截面排名）</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键发现</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>纯库存连续信号(stock_Rs100)表现优异(0.92)，双排序(stock_mom)仅略高(0.94)</li>\n<li>库存窗口80-100天最优，与研报建议的40-70天稍偏长</li>\n<li>短动量(10天)最有效，长动量(40天)反而损害表现</li>\n<li>连续化信号是R1到R2的关键转折点（Sharpe翻倍）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（60个品种有库存数据）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 双周（15天）</li>\n<li><strong>库存数据</strong>: inventory_21 (53.6%非空) + receipt (34.8%非空)</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 库存数据覆盖率有限（部分品种缺失），信号仅对有库存数据的品种有效\n<p>- 最大回撤较大(-50.9%)，需控制杠杆 - 前半段Sharpe 1.30 &gt; 后半段0.97，存在一定信号衰减 - 与因子库中 xinye_combo 因子相关性0.57（近似冗余边界）</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>R_STOCK</code></td><td><code>80</code></td><td>库存均值窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>R_MOM</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>动量回看</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>15</code></td><td>再平衡周期</td></tr><tr><td><code>FIRST_SORT_HIGH</code></td><td><code>0.6</code></td><td>rank&gt;=0.6 → low_inv (long pool)</td></tr><tr><td><code>FIRST_SORT_LOW</code></td><td><code>0.4</code></td><td>rank&lt;=0.4 → high_inv (short pool)</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9841</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.3s</li>\n</ul>"}